lead_paragraph: Coach Didier Deschamps believes his players are ready to write a new page in the history of French football at Euro 2016 on Thursday when the hosts attempt to beat Germany for the first time for 58 years in a competitive match.

headline.print_headline: France Bid to End 58-Year Run of Losing to Germans in Big Games
